					"value": "Dialogue with the ghost of Sendai, bound to eternal service to Bhaal in her afterlife. In \"Baldur's Gate 2: Throne of Bhaal\", Sendai was one of the Five, an evil group of Bhaalspawn led by Amelyssan."
